title: PHP SDKs
content:
A curated lists of PHP SDKs maintained by FPFIS :
iTopApi The plugins SDK allows for interactions with iTop CMDB.
composer require ec-europa/itopapi:~1.0  Backtrac PHP client This projects includes both a client library and a phing helper to trigger visual comparison.
composer require ec-europa/backtrac-php-client:~0.1

title: Docker images
content:
Hub All images are available on FPFIS’s Docker hub
A curated lists of docker images maintained by FPFIS
Redis Redis Docker image
docker pull fpfis/redis  Varnish Varnish Docker image
docker pull fpfis/varnish

content:
